data.description:
Can we call this Gilbert lite?  Horses and no HOA!  Exciting opportunity for horse property with Chandler schools, views of the San Tan Mountains!  Close to QC Equestrian Center this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home has new interior paint, new flooring, new HVAC, new garage door with state of art opener, newer exterior paint and roof, with a pool built in 2019!  This property is absolutely turnkey! 
Kitchen is loaded with cabinets, pot rack, separate pantry, and island.  Electrolux washer and dryer stay, as well as French door Frigidaire refrigerator.  Enjoy the Minka Aire trio of fans on covered patio!  Sheds convey as-is and Ring doorbell and Ring flood lights will convey.
Plenty of room to add animals, or home business, absorbing the country lifestyle, minutes from Seville area in Gilbert.
